{
  "stem": "3453.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a barn for cows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a double wall erected.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there a little opening, you open up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You went in down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you close.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You masqueraded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then if a soldier or somebody would walk in, he wouldn't see nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because we were-- on the-- the double wall was-- in between it in the double wall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then I walked in there, but eight or nine people were sitting down there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was inside the ghetto, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But belonged to my uncle's mother-in-law or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in fear every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, we heard that they took some people from our ghetto to build some kind of camp, a camp in the outskirts of our town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like in a-- in a little valley.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was surrounded by little hills.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- didn't have mountains, hills.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was in a little valley.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they built down there a camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Right away, we-- we were suspicious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The people who were building, asking the-- the Germans who were supervising them, what is it for.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said we are-- have to bring prisoners of war from the front in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's where we are going to keep them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- we didn't have no choice to believe them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they deceived us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was camp was erected for the people of our town, plus the people from all the small towns.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm speaking 6,000 Jewish inhabitants of ours, plus between 16 about 17,000 people, I can be shy a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They brought them in in the cattle trains, whatever we saw on television, at night from the small towns.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was close to [INAUDIBLE], [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From all the small town, they brought them in-- into Sarny.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
